Distribution. The species has been reported from the Russian Far East (
Zaslavskij 1956
), Japan (
Morimoto & Miyakawa 1985
), South Korea (
Morimoto & Lee 1992
) and NE China (
Prena 2011
). We document here its occurrence in Anhui, Beijing, Chongqing, Fujian, Gansu, Hebei, Heilongjiang, Henan, Jilin, Shaanxi, Shandong and Zhejiang (
Fig. 21
).
